    "Lexicographers are well-positioned to provide this expertise, although the demand for their skills might diminish compared to past requirements.",
    "Moreover, the role of lexicographers is evolving, necessitating a shift towards a more interdisciplinary approach that blends traditional lexicographic skills with knowledge of computational linguistics, big data, and data science (compare Grabowski, 2023).",
